{"tid":2401932,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 UST南亞仔請入","createTime":"2021-02-10T05:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T07:45:23.000Z","uid":131368,"like":29,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ebefe07d3612318bcc0e0766a6470aecd9cb638f","tid":2401932,"uid":131368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:59:14.000Z","msg":"話說今日又去食瓏門<br />\n天寒地凍原本諗住再食銷魂飯<br />\n或者常餐<br />\n又或者多肉牛肉飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fsgrxbo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFsgrxbo.jpg&h=8fbfa839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知見到隔離食滑蛋蝦仁飯<br />\n咁就勾起我食滑蛋既癮<br />\n就黎個E餐滑蛋叉燒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 但一諗起兩年前中過既伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E41yWEV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE41yWEV.png&h=7c9e95c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都有d驚 又乾又凍又瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知一上<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CyVcsNd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCyVcsNd.png&h=6d655f1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁撚靚仔架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食評<br />\n滑蛋好撚滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叉燒又多又大塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲熱既<br />\n唔好睇佢咁乾<br />\n咬落去好juicy好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加埋杯茶走<br />\n夠熱夠濃飲落去好c服<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完個刻<br />\n我又再諗<br />\n下次去瓏門應該食咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63744f0d6f5857f67fb78ac470321574671a82ba","tid":2401932,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:00:42.000Z","msg":"嚇死我 以為佢又柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64114849c92e9a19a14a2d88c24d541bd6e9af5c","tid":2401932,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"Btw 佢啲燒味的確唔錯"},{"pid":"60628f039a2d8aac313713015c56b9dcb9c30dfe","tid":2401932,"uid":131368,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"63744f0d6f5857f67fb78ac470321574671a82ba","tid":2401932,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:00:42.000Z","msg":"嚇死我 以為佢又柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:07:28.000Z","msg":"55蚊驚佢做唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15989a7a9ffa78d050e09663bb553bbe8a1e3dd7","tid":2401932,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"60628f039a2d8aac313713015c56b9dcb9c30dfe","tid":2401932,"uid":131368,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"63744f0d6f5857f67fb78ac470321574671a82ba","tid":2401932,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:00:42.000Z","msg":"嚇死我 以為佢又柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:07:28.000Z","msg":"55蚊驚佢做唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:09:19.000Z","msg":"唔會啦 